Disqualified Big Brother Naija, BBNaija housemate, Erica has said she learnt that it’s completely fine to be alone in the house. Erica, who apologised to her fans for her disqualification, said she was meant to be more responsible. In an interview with Africa Magic, Erica said “The lesson I have learnt from staying in the house is that I should be fine with being alone. “I noticed I didn’t like to be alone which is not meant to be.” She further stated that she will miss the Saturday night party and the task. Erica added that she doesn’t hate Laycon and regrets the harsh words the hurled at him.